title: [Miasmal Forest, Troll Mound]
description: Lumpy turf rises out of the marshy ground.  Spiky-leafed plants grow in clumps beneath the scraggly branches of the trees lining the pathway.  Jagged, lichen-covered rocks jab through the soil.  Fog, cool and damp, coils through the trees.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, south
